data.message: I use a digital desk tone, available on all mobiles by default, so classic, so boring, so professional. Almost never gets me silly comments when my phone rings in the middle of the office, even if I forget to set my phone to silent in a meeting and it rings, I don't get blamed as it happens to those with catchy ring tones.
A geek needs to focus, so make your phone silent :)
